description:
Season 3, episode 10 -- original air date: December 20th, 2007 (Teletoon, Canada)

Episode title: The Son also Rises

Parodies: (none obvious, appears to be original)

Bob&#039;s quote: "Peter Piper picked a peck of pickled peppers"

Summary: Chode gets contacted from a long-past ex-girlfriend, and informs him he has a son. Now suddenly a father, he is forced into custody and takes him home to the ship. An unexpected twist takes him from showing he can try to be a good father, to his old self again.
